reviews.text: It's hamburger is good. Regular size. Priced at ~$70

Tried their jalapeno mix beef burger and it was really good. Go double and the meat and spice mix make it worth the effort. The location is not the best to get to though. However, the staff is quite nice and helpful. Hopefully they can open more branches soon.
Great Burgers. Slow service
Good range of burgers and price is reasonable. The beef tastes good and the fries are thick cut so had plenty of potato taste.

Burger was nice with wide range of choices of burger. I tried their blue chesse burger. Not bad. The chips goes with set is in small portion. It was just next to the Telford cinema. No need to wait for seat and very spacious. Good to have it before or after the movie. They serve very quickly. However, it is a bit expensive.
